## dma-ranges

Defines the mapping between DMA-capable child bus addresses and parent bus addresses. Similar format to `ranges`.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
pcie0: pci@1c00000 {
    dma-ranges = <0x02000000 0x0 0x00000000 0x0 0x00000000 0x10 0x00000000>;
};
```
